                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2181" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0442</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8119 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浴火重生：六允矿业的战略变革之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Born of Fire: The Strategic Change of Liuyun Corporation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">焦豪，谢佩洪等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">六允矿业集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">矿冶业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">26 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略变革；国有企业；六允矿业；煤炭；多元化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Strategic Change, State-owned Enterprise, Liuyun Corporation, Coal Industry, Diversification</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">十八届三中全会提出改革的方向是进一步深化经济体制改革，市场的作用不断得到加强。我国企业尤其是国有企业面临的竞争将会越来越来激烈。进行变革，特别是战略变革来适应激烈的竞争变得越来越有必要。国有企业通常在关系国家经济发展的核心产业部门，对我国经济发展起到至关重要的作用。因此国有企业的战略变革需要有合理明确的目标方向和科学的规划，同时国有企业战略变革需要是全方位的优化，包裹建立起现代化企业治理方式，培育适合自身发展的企业文化，构建运营高效的组织结构，形成合理公正的人才制度。国有企业战略变革是个系统而复杂的过程，不可能一蹴而就，也不会一帆风顺。那么影响国有企业战略变革的外部环境因素和内部状况因素有哪些？企业进行改革的具体措施有哪些？战略变革的目标又是什么？这些问题值得我们去深入思考。本案例通过对六允矿业超过20年的战略变革之路进行梳理，并重点分析其最近十年的战略变革，以期为回答上述问题提供思路。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The direction of the reform is further deepening the reform of the economic system which was put forward at the 3rd Session of the 18th Central CPC. The role of the market should be continuously strengthened. Enterprises, especially state-owned enterprises will face a more intense competitive business environment in China. Change, especially strategic change, is more necessary for enterprises to adapt to fierce competition. State-owned enterprises are very important for the development of our country. It is necessary to have right directions and rational planning for the strategic change of state-owned enterprises. The strategic change of state-owned enterprises also needs to optimize other aspects, such as modern corporate governance system, suitable enterprise culture, efficient organizational structure and fair talents system. Enterprise strategic change will not happen overnight, and enterprise strategic change will not have a single confirmed result. What are the external and internal factors that will influence the state-owned enterprise strategic change? What are the specific ways of state-owned enterprise strategic change? What are the goals of state-owned enterprise strategic change? These questions are worth our deepest consideration. In order to provide ideas to answer the questions above, this article introduced the strategic change of Liuyun Corporation over 20 years, and focused on analyzing the strategic change in the past ten years of Liuyun Corporation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业管理》、《公司战略》、《管理咨询与诊断》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略变革</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015-10</td>
                            </tr>
